<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>8381</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>13687</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我的爸爸做了很长一段时间的旅行销售员。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13688</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19016</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个时候有很多的旅行销售员。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19017</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26759</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们卖工具、百科全书、唱片，甚至还卖巧克力！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26760</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32929</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我的爸爸卖小工具和工具箱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32930</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38048</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他在美国中西部的小镇和村庄之间奔走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38049</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44051</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有时，他得开车行驶几百英里的路。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50264</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他会给大家看最新的产品并介绍它们的功能。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50265</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他告诉我，他总体来说还是很成功的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59601</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他喜欢每天见到新的面孔。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63849</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他很享受他的工作。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63850</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69974</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一次，爸爸在天黑时来到了一个小镇。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69975</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74038</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他发现那个小镇只有一条街，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74039</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77615</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>街上开着几个小商店。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77616</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82261</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他走进唯一一个亮着灯的商店里，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82262</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86583</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>打算询问去往酒店的路怎么走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86584</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89878</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“晚上好，先生。”爸爸说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89879</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94088</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“晚上好！”商店老板回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94089</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96714</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我在找一个酒店。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96715</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98563</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你已经找到了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98564</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100616</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是一家酒店？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100617</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我没看到任何标牌。”爸爸说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104519</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108975</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，我们这儿是镇里唯一的酒店。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108976</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111481</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你需要一个房间吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111482</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112814</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112815</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115110</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这边请。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115111</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121948</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>酒店老板把他领到了角落里一个又小又黑的房间前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121949</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125574</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你有大一点的房间吗？”爸爸问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125575</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129371</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有。这是我们唯一的房间。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129372</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132673</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那就这间吧。”爸爸回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132674</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138762</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>到了深夜的时候，爸爸发现他一整天都没吃过东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138763</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142849</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是他回到酒店老板那里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142850</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145939</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们提供晚餐吗？”他问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145940</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148926</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，在另一个房间。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148927</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150231</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“几点？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150232</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154381</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“随时来都可以。”酒店老板说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154382</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161160</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸把行李整理好，走到了在“另一个房间”的餐厅。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161161</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167698</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>让爸爸惊讶的是，酒店老板竟然是服务员！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167699</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172493</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他问道：“可以在吐司上放香肠吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172494</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177228</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，我从来不吃香肠。”我爸爸说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177229</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180429</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“既然如此。”服务员说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180430</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185557</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“晚餐到此结束。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185558</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189538</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸对餐厅的食物非常失望，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189539</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192230</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以什么也没有吃。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192231</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195263</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他回到了房间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195264</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200558</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天，爸爸想找老板付住宿费。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200559</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204593</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把整个酒店都找遍了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204594</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212528</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他发现老板正穿着睡衣坐在客厅里的椅子上睡觉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212529</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219397</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在那时，爸爸才发现他住的地方根本不是酒店！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219398</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225292</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他一整晚都住在一个陌生人的家里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>